    <briefdescription>
<para>Adaptor exposing a 2D point cloud to nanoflann. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>This class provides the minimal interface required by nanoflann to access a set of 2D points stored as separate x and y coordinate arrays.</para>
<para>The data is not owned by the adaptor; it references external vectors. </para>
    </detaileddescription>
